<section id="about" class="container py-5">

    <h2 class="text-center mb-4">About Me</h2>

    <p>
        I am currently an Information Technology student with a strong interest
        in computer hardware, networking, and cybersecurity. I enjoy learning
        about computer assembly, hardware troubleshooting, system maintenance,
        and network configuration. Throughout my studies, I have also gained
        experience in programming and database development using C#, Python,
        Java, SQL, HTML, and CSS, allowing me to understand both the hardware
        and software aspects of information technology.
    </p>

    <p>
        My career goal is to build a successful career in cybersecurity,
        specializing in protecting computer systems, networks, and sensitive
        information from cyber threats. I am committed to continuously improving
        my knowledge of cybersecurity principles, ethical hacking, network
        security, and digital forensics while strengthening my analytical and
        problem-solving skills. Outside academics, I enjoy exploring new
        technologies, learning about the latest cybersecurity trends, gaming,
        and working on personal projects that enhance my technical and security
        expertise.
    </p>

</section>

